18.rule_text:
Action - Beckon - Aura 20
Place Archon of Light on a spot adjacent to you facing the same direction as you, then exert it. 

Swift - Holy Attack [3] - Exert 
Archon of Light deals 3 damage to a target in its awareness.

Continuous - Dark Weakness
All dark damage dealt to Archon of Light gains +1.

20.name: Defensive Practice
20.rule_text:
Swift - Defence [1] - Energy 4
Prevent the next 1 damage dealt to you until the end of the round.
20.flavour_text: They can come from any direction at any time. You need to always be ready. - Feng

58.name: Future Sight
58.rule_text:
Swift - Cast - Aura 2 
Look at the top card of target champion’s timeline.
58.flavour_text: I've seen into your future and it does not look good. ~ Nubia

36.name: Dodge
36.rule_text:
Swift - Execute - Energy 4
If you are able to move or rotate, you may move and then you may rotate.
36.flavour_text: “You’re going to have to be faster than that to hit me.” ~ Long

34.name: Concussion Punch
34.rule_text:
Action - Basic Attack [2] - Energy 5
You deal 2 damage to a target in Concussion Punch’s awareness. 

Trigger - Stun 
If a target is dealt damage by Concussion Punch this turn then they cannot move or rotate until the end of the round.
34.flavour_text: “When all else fails, just bash them in the face.” ~ Malik

31.name: Torrents
31.rule_text:
Swift - Cast - Aura 5
Negate target technique played by a champion in Torrents's awareness unless they pay Energy 5.
31.flavour_text: “Stopped by a little wind, how pathetic.” ~ Nubia

30.name: Thrust
30.rule_text:
<<You can only execute Thrust if you have executed another technique this round.>>

Swift - Basic Attack [4] - Exert and Energy 2
You deal 4 damage to a target in Thrust’s awareness.
30.flavour_text: The flames of the phoenix pierce deep through the skin and burn the soul.

29.name: Shoulder Throw
29.rule_text:
Swift - Basic Attack [2] - Energy 2
You deal 2 damage to a target in Shoulder Throw’s awareness. 

Trigger - Toss
If a champion or summon is dealt damage by Shoulder Throw then you may place it on any spot around you.
29.flavour_text: “Never sneak up on a trained warrior. It will not end well for you.” ~ Long

26.name: Holy Wall
26.rule_text:
Swift - Cast - Aura 17 
Prevent all damage dealt to a target until the end of the round.
26.flavour_text: As darkness surrounds you and you’ve lost all faith, remember that the Angels are looking down on you. ~ Nubia to Princess Odara

25.name: Guided Arrow
25.rule_text:
Swift - Range Attack [1] - Energy 2 
You deal 1 range damage to a target in Guided Arrow’s awareness.
25.flavour_text: “Vadhis soldiers train day and night. They are refined. They are precise. They are flawless. They never miss.” ~ Ra’ha

13.name: Cross Punch
13.rule_text:
Swift - Basic Attack [1] - Energy 2
You deal 1 damage to a target in Cross Punch’s awareness.
13.flavour_text: Never forget the value of mastering the basics.

52.name: Blink Shard
52.rule_text:
Swift - Cast - Aura 10 and Energy 6
Place any target in Blink Shard’s awareness onto any unoccupied spot, facing any direction.
52.flavour_text: “These little crystals contain the power of Space. With them, you can send your enemies to the furthest reaches of the world." ~ Rayne

51.name: Aura Surge
51.rule_text:
Action - Cast - Energy 5
You gain 10 Aura.
51.flavour_text: Aura is a very valuable resource. If you waste it, it can be nearly impossible to get back.

50.name: Rejuvenating Spring
50.rule_text:
Swift - Heal [3] - Aura 12 and Energy 3 
You or a target around you gains 3 HP.
50.flavour_text: Legends speak of hidden springs in the mountains with waters so full of life that if you were to drink from them, you would have all your ailments healed.

47.name: Nature's Reclaim
47.rule_text:
Action - Cast - Aura 15  
Destroy target alteration in Nature’s Reclaim's awareness.
47.flavour_text: We must find balance in the world. If we do not keep the balance then the world will do it for us. ~ Feng

45.name: Meditative Ascension
45.rule_text:
Action - Execute - Energy 7 
You cannot be targeted until the end of the round.
45.flavour_text: “Ignore the world around you. It cannot harm you. Just focus on your breath and let everything else go.” ~ Long

40.name: Flame
40.rule_text:
Action - Cast - Aura 10 
You deal 2 fire damage to a target in Flame’s awareness.
40.flavour_text: Throw caution to the wind, and throw fire at your enemies.

39.name: Fire Imbue
39.rule_text:
Action - Enchant - Energy 1 
Attach Fire Imbue as a skill. 

Continuous - Enchantment 
All attacks you do deal fire damage in addition to other types.
39.flavour_text: Let the flames from the phoenix surround you and guide your every strike. ~ Feng

23.name: Fortification
23.rule_text:
Action - Create - Aura 12
Place Fortification onto an unoccupied spot in the arena.

Continuous - Fortification
Fortification occupies the spot it is on.
23.flavour_text: “Are these walls here for our protection or our entrapment?’’ ~ Princess Odara to Kendra.

32.name: Treacherous Terrain
32.rule_text:
Swift - Create - Aura 12
Place Treacherous Terrain on an unoccupied spot in the arena.

Continuous - Treacherous Terrain
Champions and summons cannot move onto Treacherous Terrain unless they pay Energy (3) or Health (1).
32.flavour_text: The world of Jaelara is harsh, violent, and monstrous. Never underestimate it. ~ Ra'Ha

82.name: Skeleton King
82.rule_text:
<i>You can only play Skeleton King's resurect ability if another summon has been killed this round. <i>

Action - Resurrect Beckon - Aura 15
Place Skeleton King on a spot where a summon has been killed this round, facing the same direction as you, then exert it. 

Swift - Basic Attack [3] - Exert
Skeleton King deals 3 damage to a target in its awareness.

81.name: Side Swipe
81.rule_text:
Swift - Basic Attack [2] - Energy 3
You deal 2 damage to a target in Side Swipe’s awareness.

79.name: Malevolent Spirit
79.rule_text:
Action - Beckon - Aura 10 and Health 2 
Place Malevolent Spirit on a spot adjacent to you facing the same direction as you, then exert it. 

Action - Madness - Exert
Target champion in Malevolent Spirit’s awareness discards a card at random. 

Continuous - Spectral 
Malevolent Spirit cannot be targeted by Attack abilities (example: Basic Attack, Heavy Attack, Fire Attack, etc.).

59.name: Hydro Blast
59.rule_text:
Swift - Water Attack [2] - Energy 3
You deal 2 Water damage to a target in Hydro Blast’s awareness. 

Trigger - Push 
If anything is dealt damage by Hydro Blast they move one spot away from you.
